{"tid":1075901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【暴動罪重審】德國會人權主席：裁決無改中國極權事實　港人展巨大勇氣承擔","createTime":"2019-03-24T12:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T13:23:23.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ce49207f148d33f8077f08222d6b6e15602865fd","tid":1075901,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/暴動罪重審-德國會人權主席-裁決無改中國極權事實-港人展巨大勇氣承擔/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E9%87%8D%E5%AF%A9-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E8%A3%81%E6%B1%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%95%E5%B7%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%8B%87%E6%B0%A3%E6%89%BF%E6%93%94%2F&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8pKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=a0761ca4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E9%87%8D%E5%AF%A9-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E8%A3%81%E6%B1%BA%E7%84%A1%E6%94%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B1%95%E5%B7%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%8B%87%E6%B0%A3%E6%89%BF%E6%93%94%2F&h=c66f2f98\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/暴動罪重審-德國會人權主席-裁決無改中國極權事實-港人展巨大勇氣承擔/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/leung-01_HDGgs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fleung-01_HDGgs_1200x0.png&h=31b2124c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁天琦、李諾文、容偉業、林傲軒<br />\n<br />\n本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦等人被控參與旺角暴動，其中一項陪審團未達裁決的暴動罪於高等法院重審，結果梁天琦等三人罪名不成立，容偉業被判三項罪成。德國國會轄下人權及人道救援委員會主席Gyde Jensen發表聲明，指判決無改中國向香港輸出極權主義的事實，另一方面她讚揚香港公民社會展現了巨大勇氣及政治承擔。<br />\n<br />\n據關注香港人權狀況的英國組織「香港觀察（Hong Kong Watch）」表示，Gyde Jensen在上周五發表了聲明，指梁天琦被判無罪後，仍然因為早前的其他案件而繼續被監禁。她指今次的判決不改中國向香港輸出極權主義的事實，「香港的公民社會面對鎮壓的威脅時，付出巨大勇氣及政治承擔，應該獲得讚揚」。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦一案引起國際社會關注，德國另外兩位國會議員Margarete Bause及Martin Patzelt早前亦參與了，由多個國家合共 11 名國會議員發出的聯合聲明，要求香港政府改革《公安條例》。"},{"pid":"8ee10ed3de5fd93112ea3bad6e0ab5e969e26cb9","tid":1075901,"uid":199613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"由多個國家合共 11 名國會議員發出的聯合聲明<br />\n<br />\n咁都幾多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e032521027bb6e33f54f492de8829d6bce012b9","tid":1075901,"uid":157994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8ee10ed3de5fd93112ea3bad6e0ab5e969e26cb9","tid":1075901,"uid":199613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"由多個國家合共 11 名國會議員發出的聯合聲明<br />\n<br />\n咁都幾多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"人地唔同國家既議員幫你d生番追討民主喎，仲想點呀師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb05375dc64eadc59bafb9fe47c82599ea416b8a","tid":1075901,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T13:23:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}